Central bank dollar / rouble rates 5429 / 5439 . The Russian Central Bank said it had set 5429 / 5439 roubles per dollar as its bid and offer rates for its operations on the currency market on Thursday . The official rate for Friday will be 5434 . On Wednesday the bid / offer rates were also 5429 / 5439 , with the official dollar rate 5434 from Thursday . The Central Bank announces daily bid / offer dollar / rouble rates for its currency operations . The midpoint of these rates is the official dollar / rouble rate for the following day . The daily corridor for the rouble on the interbank market is 5295 / 5895 after 5292 / 5892 . - - Moscow Newsroom , + 7095 941 8520 
